column4: NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "3998AF7B48764A347AA9D99776EED080", "Hmm, you\'re something else! That was pretty good for so early in the morning.")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "E3F9DC8847CD17DC3B439AA766419A89", "Hey, hey, don\'t act like it\'s somebody else\'s business!")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "8454D2E64AB983A33A3EB59879EFCBC1", "I know! I know what you\'re talking about.")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "EB8CF7114BB241349FE80B9E019A02C4", "I hear you\'re working hard for the island by gathering Digimons.")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "688E29CE4567BE4A1230BF968735CE2E", "So you know. Well, why don\'t you help me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "BE4C9B0643D3FDB81395CCA29EA01ADB", "And, where am I supposed to do what?")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "23019CFE400EACEEA4B6489D7CD0E378", "Oh you just don\'t get it! You\'re supposed to work in the city, remember?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "6FAF55CC49CA547FF1D0459C72D9216F", "Well, like they say... the early bird gets the bug.")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "6695830E460751062590F4A6144902D0", "That has nothing to do with anything! On top of that, it\'s a worm not a bug!")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "ADD1181147B9A51DB7C659B2F8EBF694", "I\'m just joking. Well, I\'ll see you in the city...")
NSLOCTEXT("[74E3B8E9413684075A1A5D92C4423DAD]", "168A5F7146B090E365704282F7BA52F9", "Can we really trust him? I wonder...")
